---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout
  title="The Evolution — EduMyna"
  description="From a physical incubator in Kochi to an AI-first education institution. A twelve-year experiment, consciously evolving."
>

  <!-- ============================================================
       HERO
  ============================================================ -->
  <section class="relative overflow-hidden bg-myna-black min-h-[70vh] flex items-end">

    <!-- Radial amber glow -->
    <div class="absolute top-0 left-0 w-[800px] h-[800px] rounded-full pointer-events-none"
      style="background: radial-gradient(circle at top left, rgba(245,166,35,0.12) 0%, transparent 65%);">
    </div>

    <!-- Dot grid -->
    <div class="absolute inset-0 opacity-[0.035] pointer-events-none"
      style="background-image: radial-gradient(circle, #F5EFE0 1px, transparent 1px); background-size: 28px 28px;">
    </div>

    <!-- Large decorative year -->
    <div class="absolute bottom-0 right-0 text-[22rem] font-bold leading-none text-myna-amber/[0.04] select-none tracking-tighter pointer-events-none">
      2012
    </div>

    <div class="relative max-w-7xl mx-auto px-5 sm:px-8 pt-32 pb-20 lg:pb-28 w-full">

      <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 mb-8">
        <span class="h-px w-8 bg-myna-amber"></span>
        <span class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-myna-amber">
          The Evolution
        </span>
      </div>

      <h1 class="text-5xl sm:text-6xl lg:text-7xl xl:text-8xl font-bold leading-[1.02] tracking-tight text-myna-white max-w-4xl">
        An experiment,<br />
        <span class="text-myna-amber">consciously</span><br />
        evolving.
      </h1>

      <p class="mt-8 text-lg sm:text-xl text-myna-white/50 max-w-2xl leading-relaxed">
        What began in 2012 as a physical incubator in Kochi has transformed — five times — into something that could not have been predicted at the start.
        The mission stayed the same. Everything else changed.
      </p>

      <!-- Scroll indicator -->
      <div class="mt-16 flex items-center gap-4">
        <div class="flex flex-col items-center gap-1">
          <div class="w-px h-12 bg-gradient-to-b from-myna-amber to-transparent"></div>
          <span class="text-xs text-myna-white/30 uppercase tracking-widest">Scroll</span>
        </div>
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
          {["I", "II", "III", "IV", "V"].map((n) => (
            <div class="flex flex-col items-center gap-1">
              <div class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-myna-amber/40"></div>
              <span class="text-[10px] text-myna-white/20 font-bold">{n}</span>
            </div>
          ))}
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ============================================================
       MISSION CONSTANT STRIP
  ============================================================ -->
  <div class="bg-myna-amber">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-5 sm:px-8 py-5">
      <p class="text-sm font-bold text-myna-black/70 uppercase tracking-widest text-center">
        Core mission, unchanged since 2009 —
        <span class="text-myna-black">"Enable people to enable themselves through better education."</span>
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- ============================================================
       ACT I — THE PHYSICAL BEGINNING
  ============================================================ -->
  <section class="bg-myna-black relative overflow-hidden">

    <!-- Vertical timeline line -->
    <div class="absolute left-5 sm:left-8 top-0 bottom-0 w-px bg-gradient-to-b from-myna-amber/30 via-myna-amber/10 to-transparent hidden lg:block" style="left: calc((100vw - min(80rem, 100vw)) / 2 + 2rem);">
    </div>

    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-5 sm:px-8 py-20 lg:py-28">

      <!-- Act header -->
      <div class="flex items-start gap-6 lg:gap-10 mb-14">
        <div class="flex-shrink-0 relative">
          <div class="w-14 h-14 lg:w-16 lg:h-16 rounded-full bg-myna-amber flex items-center justify-center">
            <span class="text-xs font-bold text-myna-black uppercase tracking-widest">I</span>
          </div>
          <div class="absolute top-16 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 w-px h-full bg-myna-amber/20 lg:hidden"></div>
        </div>
        <div>
          <span class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-myna-amber/60 mb-2 block">
            2012 — 2015
          </span>
          <h2 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-bold text-myna-white tracking-tight leading-tight">
            The Physical<br />Beginning
          </h2>
          <p class="mt-3 text-base text-myna-white/40 font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider">
            Startup Village · Kochi
          </p>
        </div>
        <!-- Large act watermark -->
        <div class="hidden xl:block ml-auto text-[10rem] font-bold text-myna-amber/05 leading-none tracking-tighter select-none flex-shrink-0">
          I
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-10 lg:gap-16">

        <!-- Left: narrative -->
        <div class="space-y-6">
          <p class="text-base text-myna-white/65 leading-relaxed">
            In 2012, a proposal to the Government of India became India's first Public-Private-Partnership technology incubator. 10,000 square feet. ₹2.5 crore in grants. A mandate to support 48 startups over five years.
          </p>
          <p class="text-base text-myna-white/65 leading-relaxed">
            By the end, the experiment had supported <span class="text-myna-white font-semibold">500 startups</span>, created <span class="text-myna-white font-semibold">3,139 jobs</span>, and helped startups raise <span class="text-myna-white font-semibold">₹45 crores</span> in funding. The returns were extraordinary by any metric.
          </p>
          <p class="text-base text-myna-white/65 leading-relaxed">
            But success revealed the problem: every good outcome depended on a small team showing up every day for every startup. Artisanal mentorship. <span class="text-myna-amber">It couldn't scale.</span>
          </p>

          <!-- Pull quote -->
          <blockquote class="border-l-2 border-myna-amber pl-6 py-2 mt-8">
            <p class="text-xl font-bold text-myna-white leading-snug tracking-tight">
              "At scale, one person can't help a thousand people."
            </p>
            <cite class="text-sm text-myna-white/35 mt-2 block not-italic">
              The breakthrough insight, March 2015
            </cite>
          </blockquote>

          <p class="text-base text-myna-white/65 leading-relaxed">
            The January 2015 strategic decision — <em class="text-myna-white not-italic font-semibold">"student startups only"</em> — was the first deliberate narrowing of focus. Constraint, it turned out, forces clarity.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Right: stats + press -->
        <div class="space-y-4">

          <!-- Stats grid -->
          <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-3">
            {[
              { n: "500+", l: "Startups supported" },
              { n: "3,139", l: "Jobs created" },
              { n: "₹45 Cr", l: "Raised by startups" },
              { n: "2012", l: "Year it started" },
            ].map(s => (
              <div class="bg-myna-brown/20 border border-myna-brown/30 rounded-sm p-5">
                <div class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold text-myna-amber leading-none tracking-tighter">{s.n}</div>
                <div class="text-xs text-myna-white/45 mt-2 leading-snug">{s.l}</div>
              </div>
            ))}
          </div>

          <!-- Model card -->
          <div class="bg-myna-brown/10 border border-myna-brown/25 rounded-sm p-5 space-y-3">
            <div class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-myna-amber/60">The Model</div>
            {[
              ["Funding", "Government grants + CSR"],
              ["Delivery", "Physical campus, in-person mentorship"],
              ["Customer", "Any startup (all stages)"],
              ["Scalability", "Low — founder-dependent"],
            ].map(([k, v]) => (
              <div class="flex justify-between items-start gap-4 border-t border-myna-white/5 pt-3 first:border-0 first:pt-0">
                <span class="text-xs text-myna-white/35 uppercase tracking-wider flex-shrink-0">{k}</span>
                <span class="text-xs text-myna-white/70 text-right">{v}</span>
              </div>
            ))}
          </div>

          <!-- Press mentions -->
          <div class="space-y-2">
            <div class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-myna-white/25 mb-3">Press</div>
            {[
              { outlet: "BBC", label: "India's startup village", href: "https://www.bbc.com/news/business-22205601" },
              { outlet: "YouTube", label: "A school for startups", href: "https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=LCsQ68plQos" },
              { outlet: "Silicon India", label: "India's first startup village", href: "https://www.siliconindia.com/shownews/www.siliconindia.com/shownews/indias-first-startup-village-at-kochi-nid-103361-cid-100.html" },
            ].map(p => (
              <a href={p.href} target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"
                class="flex items-center gap-3 group">
                <span class="text-[10px] font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-myna-amber/50 bg-myna-amber/10 px-2 py-1 rounded-sm flex-shrink-0 group-hover:text-myna-amber transition-colors">
                  {p.outlet}
                </span>
                <span class="text-xs text-myna-white/35 group-hover:text-myna-white/60 transition-colors truncate">{p.label} →</span>
              </a>
            ))}
          </div>

        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Wave divider -->
  <div class="relative h-16 bg-myna-black overflow-hidden">
    <svg viewBox="0 0 1440 64" preserveAspectRatio="none" class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
      <path d="M0,32 C240,64 480,0 720,32 C960,64 1200,0 1440,32 L1440,64 L0,64 Z" fill="#2C1A12" opacity="0.6"/>
    </svg>
  </div>

  <!-- ============================================================
       ACT II — THE DIGITAL EXPERIMENT
  ============================================================ -->
  <section class="bg-myna-black relative overflow-hidden">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-5 sm:px-8 py-20 lg:py-28">

      <div class="flex items-start gap-6 lg:gap-10 mb-14">
        <div class="flex-shrink-0">
          <div class="w-14 h-14 lg:w-16 lg:h-16 rounded-full bg-myna-brown flex items-center justify-center">
            <span class="text-xs font-bold text-myna-white uppercase tracking-widest">II</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div>
          <span class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-myna-amber/60 mb-2 block">
            2015 — 2018
          </span>
          <h2 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-bold text-myna-white tracking-tight leading-tight">
            The Digital<br />Experiment
          </h2>
          <p class="mt-3 text-base text-myna-white/40 font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider">
            SV.CO · Bangalore
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="hidden xl:block ml-auto text-[10rem] font-bold text-myna-amber/05 leading-none tracking-tighter select-none flex-shrink-0">
          II
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-10 lg:gap-16">

        <div class="space-y-6">
          <p class="text-base text-myna-white/65 leading-relaxed">
            February 2015. Physical operations wound down. SV.CO — a pure web platform — became the future. No physical space. No mobile apps. Web-first, structured progression, cohort-based delivery.
          </p>
          <p class="text-base text-myna-white/65 leading-relaxed">
            The product evolved rapidly: startup timelines, 5/10/20/30 stage progression models, six-week cohort cycles, submission-based advancement. Students had to ship to progress.
          </p>
          <p class="text-base text-myna-white/65 leading-relaxed">
            Then came June 2017 — a trip to Silicon Valley with a student cohort. What came back wasn't enthusiasm. It was <span class="text-myna-amber">clarity about the gap.</span>
          </p>

          <blockquote class="border-l-2 border-myna-amber pl-6 py-2">
            <p class="text-xl font-bold text-myna-white leading-snug tracking-tight">
              "The Valley wasn't producing great founders because of incubators. It was producing them because the education system was building people who could actually make things."
            </p>
            <cite class="text-sm text-myna-white/35 mt-2 block not-italic">
              Post-Silicon Valley clarity session, July 2017
            </cite>
          </blockquote>

          <p class="text-base text-myna-white/65 leading-relaxed">
            November 2017: the startup narrative was officially over. A new question took its place.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="space-y-4">

          <!-- The question shift — visual card -->
          <div class="bg-myna-brown/10 border border-myna-brown/30 rounded-sm p-6">
            <div class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-myna-amber/60 mb-5">The Question That Changed Everything</div>
            <div class="space-y-4">
              <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
                <span class="text-lg text-red-400/60 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5">✕</span>
                <div>
                  <div class="text-xs text-myna-white/30 uppercase tracking-wider mb-1">Old question</div>
                  <p class="text-sm text-myna-white/50 leading-relaxed">"How do we help students start startups?"</p>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="h-px bg-myna-brown/30"></div>
              <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
                <span class="text-lg text-myna-amber flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5">→</span>
                <div>
                  <div class="text-xs text-myna-amber/60 uppercase tracking-wider mb-1">New question</div>
                  <p class="text-sm text-myna-white font-semibold leading-relaxed">"How do we help students become <em class="not-italic text-myna-amber">genuinely capable</em>?"</p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Model card -->
          <div class="bg-myna-brown/10 border border-myna-brown/25 rounded-sm p-5 space-y-3">
            <div class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-myna-amber/60">The Model</div>
            {[
              ["Funding", "Freemium + cohort fees (₹5K–₹15K)"],
              ["Delivery", "Web platform, cohort-based progression"],
              ["Customer", "Student startups exclusively"],
              ["Scalability", "Medium — platform-enabled"],
            ].map(([k, v]) => (
              <div class="flex justify-between items-start gap-4 border-t border-myna-white/5 pt-3 first:border-0 first:pt-0">
                <span class="text-xs text-myna-white/35 uppercase tracking-wider flex-shrink-0">{k}</span>
                <span class="text-xs text-myna-white/70 text-right">{v}</span>
              </div>
            ))}
          </div>

          <!-- Press -->
          <div class="space-y-2">
            <div class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-myna-white/25 mb-3">Press</div>
            {[
              { outlet: "Times of India", label: "World's first online incubator for students", href: "https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/city/kochi/sv-co-worlds-first-online-incubator-for-students-rolls-out-batch-with-32-teams/articleshow/56491170.cms" },
              { outlet: "YourStory", label: "World's first digital incubator", href: "https://yourstory.com/2016/07/startup-village" },
              { outlet: "Economic Times", label: "Going completely digital", href: "https://economictimes.indiatimes.com/et-now/tech/startup-village-coo-talks-about-going-completely-digital/videoshow/53161490.cms" },
              { outlet: "Financial Express", label: "Ranked #1 incubator in India", href: "https://www.financialexpress.com/industry/kochi-startup-village-countrys-best/325625/" },
            ].map(p => (
              <a href={p.href} target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"
                class="flex items-center gap-3 group">
                <span class="text-[10px] font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-myna-amber/50 bg-myna-amber/10 px-2 py-1 rounded-sm flex-shrink-0 group-hover:text-myna-amber transition-colors">
                  {p.outlet}
                </span>
                <span class="text-xs text-myna-white/35 group-hover:text-myna-white/60 transition-colors truncate">{p.label} →</span>
              </a>
            ))}
          </div>

        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Cream wave divider -->
  <div class="relative bg-myna-black">
    <svg viewBox="0 0 1440 80" preserveAspectRatio="none" class="w-full h-20 block" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
      <path d="M0,40 C360,80 720,0 1080,40 C1260,60 1380,30 1440,40 L1440,80 L0,80 Z" fill="#FAF7F2"/>
    </svg>
  </div>

  <!-- ============================================================
       ACT III — UNIVERSITY INTEGRATION ERA
  ============================================================ -->
  <section class="bg-myna-cream relative overflow-hidden">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-5 sm:px-8 py-20 lg:py-28">

      <div class="flex items-start gap-6 lg:gap-10 mb-14">
        <div class="flex-shrink-0">
          <div class="w-14 h-14 lg:w-16 lg:h-16 rounded-full bg-myna-black flex items-center justify-center">
            <span class="text-xs font-bold text-myna-amber uppercase tracking-widest">III</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div>
          <span class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-myna-brown/60 mb-2 block">
            2018 — 2023
          </span>
          <h2 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-bold text-myna-black tracking-tight leading-tight">
            University<br />Integration Era
          </h2>
          <p class="mt-3 text-base text-myna-black/40 font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider">
            Pupilfirst · Open Source
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="hidden xl:block ml-auto text-[10rem] font-bold text-myna-black/[0.04] leading-none tracking-tighter select-none flex-shrink-0">
          III
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-10 lg:gap-16">

        <div class="space-y-6">
          <p class="text-base text-myna-black/65 leading-relaxed">
            2018 became a year of simultaneous experiments. The team ran four partnerships at once, learning from each: Hackkar (developer hiring — failed quickly), Apple iOS School at Manipal (credit-integrated — worked), Facebook VR (mission drift — cautionary), Freshworks at Sastra (genuine alignment — success).
          </p>
          <p class="text-base text-myna-black/65 leading-relaxed">
            December 5, 2018: while building for partners, the team noticed something. The platform they'd constructed — cohort management, submission tracking, feedback loops, progression logic — was comparable to Teachable.com, then valued at over $100 million.
          </p>
          <p class="text-base text-myna-black/65 leading-relaxed">
            The decision: extract it. Open-source it. The <span class="font-semibold text-myna-black">pupilfirst.com</span> domain was registered that same day.
          </p>

          <blockquote class="border-l-2 border-myna-brown pl-6 py-2">
            <p class="text-xl font-bold text-myna-black leading-snug tracking-tight">
              "Mission alignment isn't a soft requirement — it's operational."
            </p>
            <cite class="text-sm text-myna-black/40 mt-2 block not-italic">
              Key learning from the partnership experiments
            </cite>
          </blockquote>

          <p class="text-base text-myna-black/65 leading-relaxed">
            June 27, 2019: 316 commits merged in a single day. The platform's student dashboard was rebuilt entirely. A rich curriculum system — comparable to WordPress Gutenberg — replaced what came before. The pandemic that followed didn't disrupt operations. The team had been building online-first for years.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="space-y-4">

          <!-- Experiments result card -->
          <div class="bg-white border border-myna-black/10 rounded-sm p-6">
            <div class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-myna-brown mb-5">2018 Experiments</div>
            <div class="space-y-4">
              {[
                { name: "Hackkar", result: "Closed — timing mismatch", color: "text-myna-black/40", dot: "bg-myna-black/20" },
                { name: "Apple iOS @ Manipal", result: "Worked — template established", color: "text-myna-black", dot: "bg-myna-amber" },
                { name: "Facebook VR", result: "Cautionary — mission drift", color: "text-myna-black/40", dot: "bg-myna-orange" },
                { name: "Freshworks @ Sastra", result: "Success — mission aligned", color: "text-myna-black", dot: "bg-myna-amber" },
              ].map(e => (
                <div class="flex items-start gap-3 border-t border-myna-black/5 pt-3 first:border-0 first:pt-0">
                  <div class:list={["w-2 h-2 rounded-full mt-1.5 flex-shrink-0", e.dot]}></div>
                  <div>
                    <div class:list={["text-sm font-semibold", e.color]}>{e.name}</div>
                    <div class="text-xs text-myna-black/40 mt-0.5">{e.result}</div>
                  </div>
                </div>
              ))}
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Model card -->
          <div class="bg-white border border-myna-black/10 rounded-sm p-5 space-y-3">
            <div class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-myna-brown">The Model</div>
            {[
              ["Funding", "B2B2C enterprise deals"],
              ["Delivery", "LMS platform + credit integration"],
              ["Customer", "Corporates + Universities"],
              ["Milestone", "316 commits in a single day"],
            ].map(([k, v]) => (
              <div class="flex justify-between items-start gap-4 border-t border-myna-black/5 pt-3 first:border-0 first:pt-0">
                <span class="text-xs text-myna-black/35 uppercase tracking-wider flex-shrink-0">{k}</span>
                <span class="text-xs text-myna-black/70 text-right">{v}</span>
              </div>
            ))}
          </div>

          <!-- Pupilfirst links -->
          <div class="space-y-2">
            <div class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-myna-black/25 mb-3">Platform</div>
            {[
              { outlet: "GitHub", label: "Open-source LMS (Pupilfirst)", href: "https://github.com/pupilfirst/pupilfirst" },
              { outlet: "Live", label: "pupilfirst.org", href: "https://www.pupilfirst.org/" },
              { outlet: "Times of India", label: "Facebook partnership", href: "https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/business/india-business/sv-co-facebook-to-partner-with-academia-for-tech-training/articleshow/62058516.cms" },
            ].map(p => (
              <a href={p.href} target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"
                class="flex items-center gap-3 group">
                <span class="text-[10px] font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-myna-brown/60 bg-myna-brown/10 px-2 py-1 rounded-sm flex-shrink-0 group-hover:text-myna-brown transition-colors">
                  {p.outlet}
                </span>
                <span class="text-xs text-myna-black/35 group-hover:text-myna-black/70 transition-colors truncate">{p.label} →</span>
              </a>
            ))}
          </div>

        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Dark wave back -->
  <div class="relative bg-myna-cream">
    <svg viewBox="0 0 1440 80" preserveAspectRatio="none" class="w-full h-20 block" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
      <path d="M0,40 C360,0 720,80 1080,40 C1260,20 1380,50 1440,40 L1440,80 L0,80 Z" fill="#1A1209"/>
    </svg>
  </div>

  <!-- ============================================================
       ACT IV — THE GREAT UNBUNDLING
  ============================================================ -->
  <section class="bg-myna-black relative overflow-hidden">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-5 sm:px-8 py-20 lg:py-28">

      <div class="flex items-start gap-6 lg:gap-10 mb-14">
        <div class="flex-shrink-0">
          <div class="w-14 h-14 lg:w-16 lg:h-16 rounded-full border border-myna-amber/40 flex items-center justify-center">
            <span class="text-xs font-bold text-myna-amber uppercase tracking-widest">IV</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div>
          <span class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-myna-amber/60 mb-2 block">
            2023 — 2024
          </span>
          <h2 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-bold text-myna-white tracking-tight leading-tight">
            The Great<br />Unbundling
          </h2>
          <p class="mt-3 text-base text-myna-white/40 font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider">
            Direct to Consumer · Credits
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="hidden xl:block ml-auto text-[10rem] font-bold text-myna-amber/05 leading-none tracking-tighter select-none flex-shrink-0">
          IV
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-10 lg:gap-16">

        <div class="space-y-6">
          <p class="text-base text-myna-white/65 leading-relaxed">
            November 2023: a brutally honest internal document reached its conclusion. The B2B2C university-integrated model — codenamed LITE — wasn't scaling. Universities moved too slowly. Integration was too complex. The sentence was direct: <span class="text-myna-amber font-semibold">"LITE is a failure — stop it."</span>
          </p>
          <p class="text-base text-myna-white/65 leading-relaxed">
            The new strategy: go directly to students. Sell subscriptions. Offer industry-recognized credentials alongside India's government-backed Academic Bank of Credits. Let students stack micro-credentials without a university as gatekeeper.
          </p>
          <p class="text-base text-myna-white/65 leading-relaxed">
            The philosophy crystallized: instead of fixing universities from within, go <em class="not-italic text-myna-white font-semibold">around</em> them — while simultaneously offering a path back into the formal system on the student's own terms.
          </p>

          <blockquote class="border-l-2 border-myna-amber pl-6 py-2">
            <p class="text-xl font-bold text-myna-white leading-snug tracking-tight">
              "Unbundle traditional degrees. Then offer a pathway to re-bundle them — on the student's terms."
            </p>
          </blockquote>
        </div>

        <div class="space-y-4">

          <!-- What changed / what stayed -->
          <div class="bg-myna-brown/10 border border-myna-brown/30 rounded-sm p-6">
            <div class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-myna-amber/60 mb-5">What Changed vs What Stayed</div>
            <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-4">
              <div>
                <div class="text-xs text-myna-amber/60 uppercase tracking-wider mb-3">Stayed the same</div>
                <ul class="space-y-2">
                  {["The platform", "The pedagogy", "Open-source commitment", "Teaching real skills"].map(i => (
                    <li class="flex items-center gap-2">
                      <span class="w-1 h-1 rounded-full bg-myna-amber/50 flex-shrink-0"></span>
                      <span class="text-xs text-myna-white/60">{i}</span>
                    </li>
                  ))}
                </ul>
              </div>
              <div>
                <div class="text-xs text-myna-white/30 uppercase tracking-wider mb-3">Changed</div>
                <ul class="space-y-2">
                  {["B2B2C → B2C", "Enterprise → Subscription", "University sales → Direct", "Slow → Fast"].map(i => (
                    <li class="flex items-center gap-2">
                      <span class="w-1 h-1 rounded-full bg-myna-orange/50 flex-shrink-0"></span>
                      <span class="text-xs text-myna-white/60">{i}</span>
                    </li>
                  ))}
                </ul>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Model card -->
