      <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-10 lg:gap-16">

        <div class="space-y-6">
          <p class="text-base text-myna-white/70 leading-relaxed">
            Twelve years of experiments converged into a single structural question: to reach millions of students at ₹999 per month, what would the institution need to be?
          </p>
          <p class="text-base text-myna-white/70 leading-relaxed">
            EduMyna is the answer. Not another pivot — an integration. The infrastructure from Pupilfirst, the pedagogy developed through years of cohort programs, AI-first delivery, direct-to-consumer reach, academic credit integration, and an open-source commitment built into the DNA.
          </p>
          <p class="text-base text-myna-white/70 leading-relaxed">
            The human role evolves: teachers move from grading papers to designing curriculum, mentoring complex problems, building relationships, inspiring students. Intelligent automation handles the rest.
          </p>
          <p class="text-base text-myna-white/70 leading-relaxed">
            EduMyna is registering as a <span class="text-myna-white font-semibold">Section 8 nonprofit</span>. It funds and enables education programs, builds open software, and shapes the discourse around what India's undergraduate years should mean.
          </p>

          <blockquote class="border-l-2 border-myna-amber pl-6 py-2">
            <p class="text-xl font-bold text-myna-white leading-snug tracking-tight">
              "Same mission as 2009.<br />Completely different delivery mechanism."
            </p>
          </blockquote>
        </div>

        <div class="space-y-4">

          <!-- Integration diagram -->
          <div class="bg-myna-black/20 border border-myna-amber/20 rounded-sm p-6">
            <div class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-myna-amber/70 mb-5">The Integration</div>
            <div class="space-y-3">
